   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Award Description - This is the first year of a new Partner Cooperative Agreement in Burundi.. This grant is to support USADF&apos;s in-country partner in. Funds will be used for staff salaries, office space, administrative support, program monitoring, a program audit, and capacity building.. Partner Cooperative Agreement funds the technical partner to provide grant design and implementation support to USADF&apos;s beneficiary groups.</narrative>
